===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{element}} The simplest [[alkali]] [[metal]], the lightest solid element, and the third lightest chemical element (''symbol'' Li) with an [[atomic number]] of 3.
# {{pharmaceutical drug}} [[lithium carbonate|Lithium carbonate]] or other preparations of lithium metal used to treat [[manic depression]] and [[bipolar disorder]]s.

